content: Lee Hyunwook, the Steel Emperor, was the last savior of mankind, but died. In order to change the future, the place he regressed to was… The military?!!&quotWhy here of all places?!&quotThe start of Corporal Lee Hyunwook, who gets stronger in a special way, by doing a steel mukbang!
